<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Next Step — Core Crew Logistics</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/jpeg" href="/public/img/logo.jpg" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/styles.css" />
    <script>
      setTimeout(function() {
        window.location.href = '/apply/verify';
      }, 7000);
    </script>
    <style>
      /* Fix: Back button is always visible below header on all devices */
      .fixed-back-btn {
        position: fixed;
        top: 80px; /* Adjust this if your header is taller/shorter on mobile */
        left: 1rem;
        z-index: 1200;
      }
      @media (min-width: 701px) {
        .fixed-back-btn {
          top: 100px; /* Desktop header is taller */
          left: 2rem;
        }
      }
      @media (max-width: 700px) {
        main.container .info-note-card {
          margin-top: 6.5rem !important;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <a href="/"
       class="btn ghost fixed-back-btn"
       onclick="if(document.referrer && document.referrer !== window.location.href){window.history.back();}else{window.location.href='/';} return false;">
      &larr; Back
    </a>
    <main class="container">
      <div class="info-note-card" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
        <h2>Why We Request Your Information</h2>
        <p>
          At Core Crew Logistics, we are committed to creating a safe, transparent, and efficient recruitment process. The information you provide, including your personal details, resume, supporting documents, and verification data, is essential for:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Confirming your identity and eligibility for the role.</li>
          <li>Verifying your credentials and background to ensure a secure workplace.</li>
          <li>Matching you to suitable positions based on your experience and preferences.</li>
          <li>Complying with legal and regulatory requirements for employment in logistics and transportation.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          All information is handled with strict confidentiality and used only for recruitment purposes.
          If you have any questions or concerns, please contact our team at <a href="mailto:corecrewlogistics@gmail.com">corecrewlogistics@gmail.com</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Thank you for your trust in Core Crew Logistics.
        </p>
        <div class="actions" style="margin-top:2rem;">
          <a class="btn-submit-lg" href="/apply/verify">Proceed to ID.me Verification Now →</a>
        </div>
        <p style="margin-top:1rem;color:var(--text-light);font-size:0.9em;">
          You will be redirected automatically in a few seconds...
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>